item.title: readme
item.description:
NeuxDotDev is a personal account focused on developing open-source tools and projects that are useful for both beginners and advanced users.Our main goal is to create accessible technology solutions that help solve real problems and support learning and personal development.Providing simple, practical, and relevant tools to support a variety of user needs.Money is important, but helping others and providing real benefits is our top priority. Open-source projects that are easy to learn and use Practical tools for everyday and professional needs Ideas, experiments, and contributions to the developer community We are open to collaboration. Please submit issues, pull requests, or discuss them through this repository.
For questions or ideas, please contact us via GitHub Issues.
